=head2 _story_printable

 _story_printable {topic} {story_id}

Shows a complete story, in _printer-friendly_ format.

=cut

<div class = 'story_printable'>

	{-story_body|$0|$1}

	<p>
	<div class = 'tags'>Tags: 
	{-foreach|{-story_tags|$0|$1}|
		<a href = '\{-url\|SEARCH_BY_TAG\|tag\|\$0\}'>\$0</a>|, }
	</div>
	</p>

	<hr>

	<div class = 'self_links'>
		Permanent link to this page:
		<a href='{-aurl|STORY|topic|$0|id|$1}'>{-aurl|STORY|topic|$0|id|$1}</a>
	</div>

</div>
